title: Thursday Pt1: Ravens-Buccaneers preview; Should Bills sign OBJ?
itunes:title: Thursday Pt1: Ravens-Buccaneers preview; Should Bills sign OBJ?
description:
Part One of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins with hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and Super Bowl Champion Shaun O'Hara sharing if the Baltimore Ravens or Tampa Bay Buccaneers need a win more. Peter leads "we in or we out" where everyone shares if they're "in or out" on the Buffalo Bills signing Odell Beckham Jr. Later, they all provide one scary good matchup they'll be watching this weekend and then part one of the GMFB podcast finishes up with mixed bag trivia, which focuses on quarterback controversies.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
